{"type":"message","id":"96e0c20a","parentId":"e11578e5","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:48:22.777Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:038c00f1-9881-4878-9b0a-257cb623f216 task:038c00f1-9881-4878-9b0a-257cb623f216] 诊断并修复 /api/annotations 接口问题：\n\n## 问题描述\n用户反馈 api/annotations 接口不通\n\n## 需要检查的内容\n\n1. **Nginx 配置**\n   - 检查 `/etc/nginx/nginx.conf` 中是否有 `/api/annotations` 的代理配置\n   - 检查是否应该配置为 `/abyss/api/annotations`（根据之前的小说 API 路径）\n\n2. **后端服务状态**\n   - 检查批注服务是否运行\n   - 查看服务进程和端口\n   - 检查服务日志\n\n3. **API 路径**\n   - 确认正确的 API 路径是什么\n   - 测试不同的路径组合：\n     - `/api/annotations`\n     - `/abyss/api/annotations`\n     - 其他可能的路径\n\n4. **测试 API**\n   - 使用 curl 测试各个端点\n   - 检查响应状态码\n   - 查看错误信息\n\n5. **相关文件**\n   - 批注服务代码位置\n   - 批注数据库文件\n   - 相关脚本\n\n## 修复步骤\n\n1. 诊断问题原因（配置缺失/服务未运行/路径错误）\n2. 如果是配置问题，修复 Nginx 配置\n3. 如果是服务问题，启动或重启服务\n4. 如果是路径问题，更新正确的路径\n5. 测试修复后的 API\n6. 更新 HEARTBEAT.md 记录正确的 API 路径\n\n## 输出要求\n\n1. 说明问题原因\n2. 展示修复步骤\n3. 提供测试验证结果\n4. 给出正确的 API 使用方法\nCurrent time: Wednesday, March 4th, 2026 — 7:48 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772624902775}}
{"type":"message","id":"1748736f","parentId":"96e0c20a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:48:32.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈 `/api/annotations` 接口不通，需要诊断并修复。让我系统地检查这个问题。\n\n首先，我需要：\n1. 检查 Nginx 配置，看是否有正确的代理路径\n2. 检查批注服务是否运行\n3. 测试不同的 API 路径\n4. 找到相关的服务代码和配置\n\n让我先检查 Nginx 配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，让我诊断 `/api/annotations` 接口问题。\n\n## 第一步：检查 Nginx 配置"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0bab2e70247e445db41af01c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /etc/nginx/nginx.conf | grep -A 10 \"location\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":31734,"output":137,"cacheRead":3008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772624902776}}
{"type":"message","id":"6fbb3726","parentId":"1748736f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:48:32.953Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0bab2e70247e445db41af01c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"location /novel/ {\n            alias /var/www/novel/;\n            index index.html;\n            default_type text/html;\n        }\n        \n        location = /novel {\n            return 301 /novel/;\n        }\n        \n        # EvoMap 功能文档系列\n        location /evomap-docs/ {\n            alias /var/www/kuroneko.chat/evomap-docs/;\n            index index.html;\n            default_type text/html;\n            charset utf-8;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n            autoindex on;\n        }\n        \n        location = /evomap-docs {\n            return 301 /evomap-docs/;\n        }\n        \n        # ========== Agent Game - AI 多人游戏 ==========\n        # 静态文档\n        location /agent-game/docs/ {\n            alias /root/.openclaw/workspace/agent-game/multiplayer/docs/;\n            index HOW_TO_JOIN.md;\n            default_type text/plain;\n            charset utf-8;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n            autoindex on;\n        }\n\n        # HTML 接入指南 (放在 /agent-game/ 前面优先匹配)\n        location = /agent-game/how-to-join {\n            alias /root/.openclaw/workspace/agent-game/multiplayer/public/how-to-join.html;\n            default_type text/html;\n            charset utf-8;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n        }\n\n        # 主页面 - 代理到后端服务\n        location /agent-game/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3457/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_connect_timeout 60s;\n--\n        location = /agent-game {\n            return 301 /agent-game/;\n        }\n\n        # WebSocket 端点\n        location /agent-game/ws/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3457/ws/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection \"upgrade\";\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_connect_timeout 60s;\n            proxy_send_timeout 3600s;\n--\n        location /agent-game/api/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3457/api/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods \"GET, POST, OPTIONS\";\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Headers \"Content-Type, Authorization\";\n            if ($request_method = OPTIONS) {\n--\n        location /agent-game/health {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3457/health;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n            access_log off;\n        }\n        # ========== End Agent Game ==========\n        \n        # ========== SDK 静态文件 ==========\n        location /sdk/ {\n            alias /root/login_server/frontend/static/sdk/;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n            add_header Cache-Control \"public, max-age=3600\";\n        }\n        \n        # ========== English Helper API ==========\n        location /vocab-api/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3000/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;\n        }\n--\n        location /vocab-review/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8080/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        }\n\n        # ========== Login Server - 认证服务 ==========\n        # Nuxt.js 静态资源 (放在前面优先匹配)\n        location /_nuxt/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3001/_nuxt/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        }\n        \n        # 认证 API\n        location /api/auth/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:5001/api/auth/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            \n            # CORS 支持 SDK 跨域调用\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin * always;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods \"GET, POST, OPTIONS\" always;\n--\n        location /api/annotations {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3002/api/annotations;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            \n            # CORS\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin * always;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods \"GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS\" always;\n--\n        location /auth-health {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:5001/health;\n        }\n        \n        # 根目录 - 代理到登录服务 (替代 Ludo 游戏)\n        # ========== Gateway WebSocket ==========\n        location /ws {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:18789/ws;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection \"upgrade\";\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_read_timeout 86400s;\n            proxy_send_timeout 86400s;\n--\n        location /portal {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:18789/portal;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection \"upgrade\";\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_connect_timeout 600s;\n--\n        location / {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3001/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;\n        }\n--\n        location /c6_v2/ {\n            alias /opt/c6_v2/dist/;\n            try_files $uri $uri/ /c6_v2/index.html;\n            location ~* .(js|css|png|jpg|jpeg|gif|ico|svg|woff2?)$ {\n                expires 7d;\n                add_header Cache-Control \"public, immutable\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        location /v2/api/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3010/v2/api/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Host $host;\n        }\n        # ========== End 文明精铺 V2 ==========\n\n--\n        location /remote-console/ {\n            auth_basic \"Remote Console\";\n            auth_basic_user_file /etc/nginx/.htpasswd_remote_console;\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8082/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n        }\n\n--\n        location /remote-console/ws {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3003;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;\n            proxy_set_header Connection \"upgrade\";\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n            proxy_read_timeout 86400;\n            proxy_send_timeout 86400;\n--\n        location /remote-console/sdk/ {\n            alias /root/remote-console/sdk/;\n            add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;\n            add_header Cache-Control \"public, max-age=3600\";\n        }\n\n        # ========== 2026蛇年人格测试 ==========\n        location /snake-quiz/ {\n            proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8083/;\n            proxy_http_version 1.1;\n            proxy_set_header Host $host;\n            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n        }\n        # ========== End 蛇年人格测试 ==========\n\n        # ========== Civilization Roguelike ==========\n        location = /c6 {\n            return 301 /c6/;\n        }\n        location /c6/ {\n            alias /home/publish/c6/;\n            index index.html;\n            gzip on;\n            gzip_min_length 1024;\n            gzip_types application/javascript application/json application/octet-stream;\n            expires 7d;\n        }\n        # ========== End Civilization Roguelike ==========\n\n        # ========== WeChat Verify File ==========\n        location = /2d92ba91ea0f99eba190e496b00a6ef7.txt {\n            default_type text/plain;\n            return 200 fcd8edaef57222102e0683b49548dd0082e71cf7;\n        }\n        # ========== End WeChat Verify File ==========\n\n    # ========== 深渊代行者批注系统 API ==========\n    location /abyss/api/ {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3002/api/;\n        proxy_http_version 1.1;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n        \n        # CORS\n        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin * always;\n        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods \"GET, POST, PATCH, DELETE, OPTIONS\" always;\n--\n    location = /abyss/admin {\n        return 301 /abyss/admin.html;\n    }\n    \n    location /abyss/ {\n        alias /var/www/novel/abyss/;\n        index index.html;\n        default_type text/html;\n        location ~* \\.(html|css|js|json)$ {\n            expires 1h;\n        }\n    }\n    # ========== End 深渊代行者 ==========\n\n    # ========== OpenCat Portable Server ==========\n\n    location /opencat/admin {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3080/admin;\n        proxy_http_version 1.1;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n    }\n\n    location /opencat/chat {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3080/chat;\n        proxy_http_version 1.1;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n    }\n\n    location /opencat/api/ {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3080/api/;\n        proxy_http_version 1.1;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n    }\n\n    location /opencat/v1/ {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3080/v1/;\n        proxy_http_version 1.1;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n        proxy_buffering off;\n        proxy_cache off;\n        proxy_read_timeout 300s;\n    }\n--\n    location /opencat/health {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3080/health;\n        proxy_http_version 1.1;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n    }\n\n    location /opencat/openclaw {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:3080/openclaw;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;\n    }\n    # ========== End OpenCat ==